B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-9\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_9-0\">9.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_9-1\">9.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_9-2\">9.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_9-3\">9.3</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_9-4\">9.4</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_9-5\">9.5</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_39\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 39\">Chapter 39</a>, Cersei IX.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd65.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-10\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd65.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_10-0\">10.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd65.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_10-1\">10.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_65\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 65\">Chapter 65</a>, Cersei II.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404040218\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.135 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.331 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 3076/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 12537/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 28592/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 5628/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 12/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 14760/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.170/7.000 s